  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Attack is a collectible card-based roguelike game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Card Attack, there are 54 unique cards. However, you won't start with all of them. Your journey begins with just 10 cards in your deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if your initial cards seem weak, don’t worry—take on battles and push forward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through your adventure, you’ll earn additional cards as rewards. By building up your collection of reward cards, you'll soon discover the powerful 'Gabee' character waiting to join your team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW TO PLAY:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attacking with Cards:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat is turn-based. Take your time to observe your opponent's stamina and strike using your powerful red attack cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/c7ddb42533fb7f17b902dd9738c87555.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/c7ddb42533fb7f17b902dd9738c87555.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/c7ddb42533fb7f17b902dd9738c87555.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defending with Cards:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double-click on a defense card to equip its armor, reducing the damage from enemy attacks to a minimum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/2ffd74d5cc42d3a42d765189b60b173f.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/2ffd74d5cc42d3a42d765189b60b173f.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/2ffd74d5cc42d3a42d765189b60b173f.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade with Equipment/Relics:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance, reset, recover, or weaken—use your skill cards to deal devastating critical hits to your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/a3d4cd0bc9e704785e36fb5ff954d15e.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/a3d4cd0bc9e704785e36fb5ff954d15e.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/a3d4cd0bc9e704785e36fb5ff954d15e.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Acquisition (Draws):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you defeat a monster, you'll earn additional cards as rewards. Cards are suggested randomly. Choose the one that best fits your strategy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/e4758f5791157236f061238227dee288.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/e4758f5791157236f061238227dee288.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/e4758f5791157236f061238227dee288.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camping (Recovery):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop by the camp before battles to restore your health. Use the gold you've collected to recharge and prepare for the fight ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/4580ed426c8b7c56f112a694f9670eb1.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/4580ed426c8b7c56f112a694f9670eb1.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/4580ed426c8b7c56f112a694f9670eb1.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shop (Upgrades):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After every five stages, you'll encounter a shop. Don’t skip it! Use the opportunity to remove unnecessary cards, purchase new ones, and acquire valuable relics. With every upgrade, you'll grow stronger, paving the way to complete Season 1 with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/ea0e1eb6870e545e71e93404bb4b66d6.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/ea0e1eb6870e545e71e93404bb4b66d6.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/ea0e1eb6870e545e71e93404bb4b66d6.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demo Content:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience stages 1 to 10, culminating in the thrilling first boss battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the boss and feel the electrifying excitement of Card Attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/fe295d11896baffc7b57bd43a47d5647.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=950 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Attack is a collectible card-based roguelike game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Card Attack, there are 54 unique cards. However, you won't start with all of them. Your journey begins with just 10 cards in your deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if your initial cards seem weak, don’t worry—take on battles and push forward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through your adventure, you’ll earn additional cards as rewards. By building up your collection of reward cards, you'll soon discover the powerful 'Gabee' character waiting to join your team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW TO PLAY:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attacking with Cards:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat is turn-based. Take your time to observe your opponent's stamina and strike using your powerful red attack cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/c7ddb42533fb7f17b902dd9738c87555.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/c7ddb42533fb7f17b902dd9738c87555.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/c7ddb42533fb7f17b902dd9738c87555.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defending with Cards:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double-click on a defense card to equip its armor, reducing the damage from enemy attacks to a minimum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/2ffd74d5cc42d3a42d765189b60b173