\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/e4758f5791157236f061238227dee288.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camping (Recovery):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stop by the camp before battles to restore your health. Use the gold you've collected to recharge and prepare for the fight ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/4580ed426c8b7c56f112a694f9670eb1.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/4580ed426c8b7c56f112a694f9670eb1.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/4580ed426c8b7c56f112a694f9670eb1.mp4?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shop (Upgrades):</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After every five stages, you'll encounter a shop. Don’t skip it! Use the opportunity to remove unnecessary cards, purchase new ones, and acquire valuable relics. With every upgrade, you'll grow stronger, paving the way to complete Season 1 with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/ea0e1eb6870e545e71e93404bb4b66d6.poster.avif?t=1738643575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414840/extras/ea0e1eb6870e545e71e93404bb4b66d6.webm?t=1738643575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st